# Graph Layer Boundary

| Layer | Tool | Answers |
|-------|------|---------|
| Structural | `code-graph-rag` MCP | Where in code? Who imports? Blast radius? |
| Episodic | `graphiti-memory` MCP | What did we decide? ADRs? CI gotchas? |
| Git resume | `memory-bank/` | Where we left off — zero LLM |
| Static law | rules / AGENTS.md | Non-negotiable instructions |

## Repo overlay

PlasticOS repos also load **`.cursor/rules/87-plasticos-code-graph-rag.mdc`** — grep-first discipline for IB-Odoo_19.

## MUST NOT

- Use Graphiti for symbol location or import graphs
- Use code-graph for ADR/decision recall
- Collapse the two MCP servers into one mental model

MCP names: `code-graph-rag` vs `graphiti-memory` — distinct in `~/.cursor/mcp.json`.
